# Server vs Client Boundary

## Larangan

File yang diimpor hook/`"use client"` **tidak boleh** mengimpor:

- `@/lib/db/prisma`
- `@prisma/client` (kecuali `import type`)
- Paket Node (`pg`, `fs`, `dns`, …)

## Pola pemisahan

```
lib/purchasing/permintaan-group-types.ts   # types, constants, helpers murni — AMAN client
lib/purchasing/permintaan-groups.ts        # fetchPermintaanGroups + prisma — SERVER ONLY
app/api/purchasing/permintaan/groups/route.ts
app/.../hooks/usePermintaanGroups.ts         # import hanya dari *-types.ts + fetch API
```

## Checklist file baru di `lib/`

1. Butuh database? → file terpisah tanpa export ke client.
2. Types/constants dipakai UI? → `*-types.ts` tanpa import prisma.
3. Hook client → `fetch('/api/...')` saja.

## UI server-only

Badge/helper React tanpa DB boleh di `lib/{modul}/*-status.tsx` asalkan hanya import types.
